name: FlYbYcItY
description:
Considerable amount of flashing lights.

A frog on an airplane

full of flies in disguise

gets found out and is

in for a big surprise...


Worked on this for Frog jam with a group of friends. We  have never worked with unity or worked on anything this quick. it ended up being interesting so it was a real hoot to create and play.
